            <col halign="center"/>

            <row bottom="minor">
              <cell right="medium"><line>I am making apple pie and apple turnovers.</line><line>One recipe calls for 2 apples. The other</line><line>recipe calls for 3 apples. I'm making 5</line><line>recipes of each dessert. How many apples</line><line>do I need?</line></cell>
              <cell right='minor'><m>2 + ( 3 \times 5 )</m></cell>
            </row>
            <row bottom='minor'>
              <cell right="medium"><line>I have 2 one-dollar bills and 3 five-dollar</line><line>bills. How much money do I have?</line></cell>
