            </row>
            <row bottom='minor'>
              <cell right="medium"><line>Mom lets me keep any money I find when I</line><line>clean the house. She also quadruples any</line><line>money I find to pay me for my work. I</line><line>found $2 in the couch and $3 in my dad's</line><line>jacket. How much money will I have after</line><line>Mom pays me?</line></cell>
              <cell right='minor'><m>2 + 3 \times 5</m></cell>
            </row>
            <row bottom='minor'>
              <cell right="medium"><line>I need 2 cups of almond flour to make a</line><line>batch of pancakes and 3 cups of almond</line><line>flour to make a cake. I'm going to make 5</line><line>cakes and 1 batch of pancakes. How much</line><line>flour will I need?</line></cell>
